      "rationale": "Point-to-point comparison of surrogate predictions against CFD reference values on the holdout set shows maximum relative error of 3.8% at any single operating point. Mean relative error across the envelope is 1.4%. The R² of 0.984 confirms strong predictive fidelity. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at all five operating points."
