    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The MLP surrogate model satisfies all seven assessed credibility factors at or above the required level for MRL 2. Holdout set performance (MAE = 0.0031 RH, RMSE = 0.0047 RH, R² = 0.984) demonstrates strong predictive fidelity against CFD reference values across the full COU operating envelope. The worst-case RH prediction of 0.87 satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim.",
